quickview_content.productComments: Lovely Ottoman.  Good size and good value for money.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: 124.5cm Wide Tufted Rectangle Solid Colour Ottoman with Storage

quickview_content.productComments: Great fabric.  It is sturdy with good storage. It looks great in my garden room!

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Thierry 121cm Wide Velvet Tufted Rectangle Solid Colour Ottoman with Storage

quickview_content.productComments: Looks amazing

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Patil 102cm Wide Rectangle Solid Colour Footstool Ottoman with Storage
features_array: 92 x 31cm inner compartment: This storage seat offers handy holding room for smaller items.
Padded top: Sit on this ottoman comfortably, with the linen-look upholstery feeling smooth on the skin.
Steel legs: Supports this storage stool, whether sitting on it or using it for storage.
Dimensions: 44H x 102W x 40Dcm. Inner storage: 22H x 92W x 31Dcm. Maximum load 150kg. Assembly required.

quickview_content.productComments: I bought this about 6 months ago and liked it so much so I bought a second.  Only criticism I have is that one of the feet holes in both didn’t line up but we coped.  Also one lid lift higher than the other, so one is a little more difficult to open.  Nevertheless I still give 5* for easy way of ordering and delivery.  I did pay extra for 3 year warranty.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Forestburgh 90cm Wide Velvet Tufted Rectangle Solid Colour Footstool Ottoman

quickview_content.productComments: Excellent service and item exactly as described. Looks beautiful in its new home.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Amelie 71cm Wide Rectangle Solid Colour Standard Ottoman with Storage

quickview_content.productComments: Really happy with service provided. Item was received very fast. The quality of the ottoman is great. Very easy to assemble. Very pleased with product. Ties the room together its comfortable and the bonus of storage is fantastic. Really reccomend wayfair. No issues with delivery unlike some other places on the highstreet. Will use again. Thank you very much

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Cheeseman Storage Ottoman

quickview_content.productComments: Easy to put together. Only have one issue and that is a few of the screws were never put in the hinges for the lid. For price of the item you would expect better quality control.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Lavora 114cm Wide Velvet Rectangle Chequered Cube Ottoman with Storage
features_array: Colour block design: Striking and fun velvet storage box - something to bring a touch of character into your home and living spaces.
Inner 40 x 105 cm storage: Room for keeping soft furnishings and more, this storage ottoman is great for keeping your home clear of smaller pieces.
Padded top: Sit on this ottoman storage box for a temporary, comfortable seat when you need one.
Wooden legs: Proper support for this ottoman storage bench.
Dimensions: 1147H x 4W x 47D cm. Maximum load 150kg. Assembly required.

quickview_content.productComments: I love this storage ottoman, will definitely recommend to anyone who is interested. I have been searching for this type of ottoman and finally found it, it is a beautiful addition to my house.  I truly love shopping from Wayfair.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Caver 98cm Wide Rectangle Solid Colour Ottoman with Storage

quickview_content.productComments: Lovely colour - more mustard than it looks in picture which is exactly what we needed. Easy to fit legs and feels quite sturdy to sit on, with adequate padding.  Good sized storage for DVDs and board games etc. Also, looks like it will be easy to recover in future if we redecorate or the cats ruin it! Good value compared to others we were looking at. Only lost a star as hinges a bit stiff and not sure how sturdy the will be over time....

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Adheen Set of 2 Boucle Fabric Storage Footstool Ottomans

quickview_content.productComments: Love these. Beautiful footstools. Solid and such good quality. Lovely statement pieces.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Avdain 110cm Wide Velvet Rectangle No Pattern Standard Ottoman with Storage

quickview_content.productComments: Really good quality and looks expensive

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Adheen Velvet Fabric Storage Ottoman

quickview_content.productComments: Fabulous service received from wayfair.Unfortunately , the mirror arrived effective and the agent I spoke to issued me an immediate refund of almost one hundred pounds couldn't have wished for more absolutely , fantastic customer service

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Maliyah 78cm Wide Velvet Oval Solid Colour Ottoman with Storage

quickview_content.productComments: Lovely well made unit, yet light to lift which is a bonus, as easy to move around. Slightly smaller than I expected but think that’s due to the rounded edges. Looks nice in living room and sturdy enough for additional seating if needed.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Ahri 98cm Wide Rectangle Solid Colour Standard Ottoman with Storage
features_array: Upholstered in a strong textured fabric

quickview_content.productComments:
It’s a very sturdy Ottoman, lovely colour, loads of space for storage  comfy to sit on.
Well worth paying a little more to get this one as it’s worth every penny. It’s solid  the hinges are solid  work well.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: 100cm Wide Velvet Rectangle Solid Colour Ottoman with Storage

quickview_content.productComments: good quality love it delivered very quickly also , not in place yet as decorating but will look lovely

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Artis 81cm Wide Rectangle Solid Colour Footstool Ottoman

quickview_content.productComments: Lovely stool the grandchildren sit on when they come to visit also great use for my husband to put the remote on so it doesn't get lost down the sofa

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Peachey 76cm Wide Velvet Rectangle Solid Colour Standard Ottoman with Storage

quickview_content.productComments: Love the blush colour.  Nice sturdy lid and roomy inside.  Looks very good quality.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Baucau 90.5cm Wide Tufted Rectangle Solid Colour Ottoman with Storage

quickview_content.productComments: Brilliant quality and love the style. It did come up slightly larger than the dimensions, I believe it was a couple more cm in length than stated. Fortunately we had a little wiggle room love this ottoman. Glad we went for the darker option ❤️

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Gaudreau 90cm Wide Velvet Tufted Rectangle Solid Colour Ottoman

quickview_content.productComments: Beautiful ottoman. Looks perfect in my living room. The quality is superb and looks far more expensive than it cost. I am very satisfied with my purchase.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: 91cm Wide Tufted Rectangle Solid Colour Standard Ottoman with Storage

quickview_content.productComments: Good quality just right  product

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Claria 76Cm Tufted Round Storage Ottoman

quickview_content.productComments: Ordered Tuesday early evening,delivered midday Wednesday! Wife very pleased with it,delighted!

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Artus 49cm Wide Rectangle Solid Colour Ottoman with Storage

quickview_content.productComments: I am very pleased with this footstool, it is just what I needed to rest my aching legs and feet and with the added bonus of storage inside great for magazines, books etc. it is very well made not flimsy and at a really good price so I would recommend to anyone looking for a footstool

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Geonte 100cm Wide Velvet Rectangle Solid Colour Standard Ottoman with Storage

quickview_content.productComments: Very nice ) loads space very happy

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Steuben 80cm Wide Tufted Rectangle Solid Colour Footstool Ottoman

quickview_content.productComments: Excellent quality fast and efficient delivery

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Kremer 80cm Wide Velvet Tufted Rectangle Solid Colour Cocktail Ottoman

quickview_content.productComments: Amazing quality

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Pataskala 102cm Wide Velvet Tufted Rectangle Solid Colour Ottoman with Storage

quickview_content.productComments: Lovely ottoman storage box. I use it for my kids toys in the living room as I like them hidden. Also it becomes an additional seating area. I chose the colour red, however the colour is more burgundy than deep red, which I found disappointing. Also in the notes it says part assembled, however mine came fully assembled and with a piston, so when opened, it stays opened, which helps my one year old when looking for a specific toy.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Frankllin 84cm Wide Tufted Rectangle Solid Colour Footstool Ottoman
features_array: Anti slip pads on the bottom of the frame prevent scratches
Super easy assembly by attaching the frame
Upholstered in durable linen fabric that is highly wear resistant

quickview_content.productComments: Stunning table  footstool would highly recommend

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Bourquin 33cm Wide Velvet Tufted Square Footstool Ottoman with Storage

quickview_content.productComments:
Perfect size  look and feel. 
Matches my living room and provides the pop of colour I wanted.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Deane 102Cm Wide Tufted Rectangle Storage Ottoman

quickview_content.productComments: Very happy with this Ottoman with no difference in the colour as shown. Looks great with all my other purchases. The opening  closing mechanism is very smooth  not what I had been expecting

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Amberella 36 Wide Ottoman
features_array: Hidden storage: This pouf footstool has storage underneath the top lid, so you can hold blankets, books, or remote controls that need to be put away
Stable base: This stool with storage can hold up to 120kg. Non-slip foot pads prevent your floor from scratches.
Dimensions: Overall Dimensions: 36W x 36D x 44Hcm. Weight Capacity: 120kg. No assembly is required.

quickview_content.productComments: Nice

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Monica 100cm Wide Velvet Tufted Oval Solid Colour Standard Ottoman

quickview_content.productComments: Such a lovely colour of grey and size is perfect.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Starke 109cm Wide Rectangle Solid Colour Standard Ottoman with Storage

quickview_content.productComments: The piece of furniture in itself is really nice.  However, I do advise everyone to check it for flaws before putting together as we didn't (an error of judgement on our part) and only noticed after putting it together it had a tear in the fabric. Also the fitting to attach the gas spring on the lid was at a ninety degree angle.  The fitting was fortunately able to be fixed.  Maybe better packaging would have helped.  I'm still giving it four stars as I like the look of the ottoman and felt if there had been no damage it was would be worth the money.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: 103.9cm Wide Oval Solid Colour Standard Ottoman

quickview_content.productComments: Exactly like the picture! The Footstool is very light to move around but is sturdy and of excellent quality! Can’t fault this item!

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Maegan 38cm Wide Velvet Round Solid Colour Ottoman with Storage

quickview_content.productComments: Absolutely luxurious, soft and velvety on the outside. Inside perfect for storing my throws. Very pleased indeed and definitely recommend to anyone.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: 70.5cm Wide Tufted Square No Pattern Ottoman with Storage

quickview_content.productComments: I needed an ottoman for my new sofa, to stretch my legs, and after much research I chose this grey ottoman. I love  the dark grey colour, and the overall style. It was easy to install the legs, and it's a lovely size. It's firm, but also comfortable to sit on. There's lots of inside space to store blankets, books etc. So happy I bought it before it went out of stock!

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Ayrian 43cm Wide Tufted Round Solid Colour Ottoman
features_array: Modern style with a unique channel design
Felt padded feet avoid scratches on the floor
Padded with foam and upholstered in teddy bear fur fabric for a high level of comfort

quickview_content.productComments: I am obsessed. I’ve been wanting this for the longest time and I finally caught it. It’s so soft and the quality is amazing.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Aciel Bubbly Velvet Large Footstool
features_array: Accent your room with a touch of colour

quickview_content.productComments: The best buy i've made in a while.  Exactly what I was looking for, in fact better .  I had been looking for a while and came across Wayfair then this footstool.  Perfect height, length and available in great non boring colours.  I have a medical condition and often have to rest my legs in an elevated position.  This stool is perfect and I couldnt believe the low price compared to many others I had viewed.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Gershwin 30cm Wide Velvet Tufted Square Footstool Ottoman with Storage

quickview_content.productComments: Quite disappointed that this is so small. I ordered it as a footstool and to store throws in but it just isn’t big enough! Very cute though so I’ve decided to keep it as my grandson loves it. Beware though - don’t order if you want to store anything other than a couple of remotes or small toys.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Germain Square Solid Colour Footstool Ottoman

quickview_content.productComments: Brought the green absolutely stunning and chunky looks and feel expensive, I use mine as a seat when I paint or play my drums. Will buy a small cushion to protect from staims and give padding but as a footstool no need.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Kynder 76cm Wide Faux Leather Rectangle Solid Colour Ottoman with Storage

quickview_content.productComments: Solid, nice looking storage/ottoman. I have placed a grey faux fur rug over it and not only does it look great it feels nice on your feet when you use it as a footstool! Excellent value for money and quick delivery!

browse_grid_objects.product_name: 69.85cm Wide Rectangle Floral Footstool Ottoman with Storage

quickview_content.productComments: Lovely storage ottoman, quite compact but suitable for our needs. Feels well made. Overall very happy with this purchase.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: 69.85cm Wide Rectangle Solid Colour Footstool Ottoman with Storage
88.9cm Wide Tufted Rectangle Solid Colour Standard Ottoman with Storage

I definitely recommend and will be buying another one to fit more toys in

<script async>window.wf_pixel_generic_signifyd = (data) => {
  // if store_id is missing
  if (!data.store_id) {
    return;
  }

  const generateRandomGuid = () => {
    return 'xxxxxxxx-xxxx-4xxx-yxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx'
    .replace(/[xy]/g, function (c) {
        const r = Math.random() * 16 | 0,
            v = c == 'x' ? r : (r & 0x3 | 0x8);
        return v.toString(16);
    });
  }

  /**
   * This function retrieves a cookie if it exists.
   *
   * @param {String} key cookie name being fetched
   *
   * @returns cookie value
   */
  const getCookie = (key) => {
    const cookieEntry = document.cookie.split(';').find(attribute => {
      return attribute.trim().startsWith(key + '=');
    });

    return cookieEntry ? cookieEntry.split('=')[1] : null;
  }

  /**
   * This function saves a cookie with a explicit expiration time. Returns true on success.
   *
   * @param {String} cookieKey              cookie name
   * @param {String} cookieValue            cookie value
   * @param {Number} expirationMilliseconds expiration time in milliseconds
   * @param {Object} attributes             cookie attributes map
   *
   * @returns boolean true if cookie was succesfully saved.
   */
  const setCookie = (cookieKey, cookieValue, expirationMilliseconds, attributes = {}) => {
    // reject calls without key, value, or expiration time
    if (!cookieKey || !expirationMilliseconds) {
      return false
    }

    // convert attributes into cookie attributes
    const cookieAttributes = Object.entries(attributes).reduce((attributesArray, [attributeKey, attributeValue]) => {
      if (attributeValue !== null) {
        attributesArray.push(`${attributeKey}=${attributeValue}`);
      } else {
        // don't insert empty value if there is no value
        attributesArray.push(attributeKey);
      }

      return attributesArray
    }, []).join(';');

    // add expiration milliseconds onto the current milliseconds. Date() handles the carryover logic.
    const expirationDate = new Date();
    expirationDate.setTime(expirationDate.getTime() + expirationMilliseconds);

    document.cookie = `${cookieKey}=${cookieValue};expires=${expirationDate};${cookieAttributes}`;

    return true;
  }

  // ===============================================================================
  // Start of business logic

  // 24 hour timeout before resetting session cookie
  const cookieTimeoutInMilliseconds = 24 * 60 * 60 *  1000;
  // check every 10 seconds if the cookie has been cleared.
  const cookieCheckTime = 10 * 1000;

  // Boolean for checking if signifyd script has been imported
  let scriptTag = document.getElementById('sig-api');

  // set the session cookie if necessary with 24 hour timeout. This will be used by fraud team.
  // reset the cookie if a purchase occured
  let cookieValue = getCookie('FVSID');
  if (!cookieValue || data.purchase) {
    cookieValue = `${data.store_id}-${generateRandomGuid()}`;

    // set new cookie value and set new script attribute value
    setCookie('FVSID', cookieValue, cookieTimeoutInMilliseconds);
    // this will reset the cookie on purchase if the script already exists
    if (!!scriptTag) {
      scriptTag.setAttribute('data-order-session-id', cookieValue);
    }
  }

  // signifyd script has already been imported, return and don't create new script or setInterval
  if (!!scriptTag) {
    return;
  }

  // Import the signifyd script with expected attributes
  scriptTag = document.createElement('script');
  scriptTag.defer = true;
  scriptTag.type = 'text/javascript';
  scriptTag.id = 'sig-api';
  scriptTag.setAttribute('data-order-session-id', cookieValue);
  scriptTag.src = 'https://cdn-scripts.signifyd.com/api/script-tag.js';
  document.head.appendChild(scriptTag);

  // check every ten seconds and set cookie if missing (accounts for 24 hour timeout)
  setInterval(() => {
    const cookieExists = getCookie('FVSID');

    // only set a new cookie if no cookie currently exists
    if (!cookieExists) {
      const newCookieId = `${data.store_id}-${generateRandomGuid()}`;

      // set new cookie value and set new script attribute value
      setCookie('FVSID', newCookieId, cookieTimeoutInMilliseconds);
      scriptTag.setAttribute('data-order-session-id', newCookieId);
    }
  }, cookieCheckTime);
};
